author: Al Jazeera
title: UK PM fights worsening coronavirus symptoms in intensive care
description: Boris Johnson, who has spent two nights in hospital, has received oxygen but is not on a ventilator, says minister.
content:
London, United Kingdom - UK Prime Minister Boris Johnson is battling worsening coronavirus symptoms in an intensive care unit at a London hospital.
